  "detailed_description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099790/extras/0642fc7fce18223a0dac0ad776503159.webp?t=1772418567\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>Four girls find their way into an abandoned hospital, each for her own reasons.<br>Will they manage to unravel the dark secrets hiding within, escape safely, and return to their normal, peaceful lives?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099790/extras/10a4458b75462c71f635abca9873f614.webp?t=1772418567\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>This game is a horror adventure with RPG elements.<br>Look for items, solve puzzles, run from mysterious monsters, or sometimes even confront them!<br>Do everything you can to escape!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099790/extras/988a4aff11e4d06fc8091ce64493e363.webp?t=1772418567\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lots of amazing pixel art<br></li><li>4 different heroines with 4 unique aspects of one overarching tale<br></li><li>A story that is sometimes funny, sometimes endearing, sometimes sad, but never hopeless<br></li><li>Horrifying & bizarre aplenty</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099790/extras/0642fc7fce18223a0dac0ad776503159.webp?t=1772418567\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>Four girls find their way into an abandoned hospital, each for her own reasons.<br>Will they manage to unravel the dark secrets hiding within, escape safely, and return to their normal, peaceful lives?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099790/extras/10a4458b75462c71f635abca9873f614.webp?t=1772418567\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>This game is a horror adventure with RPG elements.<br>Look for items, solve puzzles, run from mysterious monsters, or sometimes even confront them!<br>Do everything you can to escape!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099790/extras/988a4aff11e4d06fc8091ce64493e363.webp?t=1772418567\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lots of amazing pixel art<br></li><li>4 different heroines with 4 unique aspects of one overarching tale<br></li><li>A story that is sometimes funny, sometimes endearing, sometimes sad, but never hopeless<br></li><li>Horrifying & bizarre aplenty</li></ul>",
